HEADWORD: Exundate
<hw>Ex*un"date</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>exundatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>exundare</ets> to overflow;
<ets>ex</ets> out + <ets>undare</ets>. See <er>Undated</er>
waved.]</ety> <def>To overflow; to inundate.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
